1
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:53,600
Diyun.

2
00:00:53,720 --> 00:00:54,650
Why are you here?

3
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:57,700
Are these medicinal herbs dried?

4
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:59,720
I'll send them over by sunset.

5
00:01:00,120 --> 00:01:01,380
Is your injury healed?

6
00:01:02,480 --> 00:01:03,400
I'm okay.

7
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,560
If I didn't owe Yunyuan a favor,

8
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:07,690
I wouldn't stay here doing hard labor.

9
00:01:07,720 --> 00:01:08,580
As for Yunyuan,

10
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:10,120
the rebuilding of Shishannan Village

11
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:11,760
is all being managed by him alone.

12
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:13,600
He lives up to his reputation as the revered King Kunmi.

13
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:14,400
On this point,

14
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:15,800
I, Diyun, admire him.

15
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:17,450
However,

16
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:20,080
I will absolutely not give you up to him.

17
00:01:20,360 --> 00:01:22,160
Why are you dragging me into this again?

18
00:01:22,160 --> 00:01:24,880
I thought you two had buried the hatchet.

19
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:26,480
I am a living person.

20
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:27,440
You keep fighting over me,

21
00:01:27,440 --> 00:01:28,700
what do you take me for?

22
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:30,200
Say, Little Highness,

23
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:32,060
did you catch the snake demon?

24
00:01:34,039 --> 00:01:35,560
That snake demon is very cunning.

25
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,620
It has many clones.

26
00:01:36,960 --> 00:01:39,490
How could you fail to catch a mere snake demon?

27
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:41,240
I...

28
00:01:41,440 --> 00:01:42,120
Qingluan.

29
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:46,610
Yueying.

30
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:48,160
Yueying, what's wrong?

31
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:49,020
Save him first.

32
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:50,650
Yueying.

33
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:53,600
Brother.

34
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:54,840
Yueying is critically injured.

35
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,039
Return immediately.

36
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:04,560
Sister Qingluan,

37
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:07,040
who on earth could injure Yueying so severely?

38
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,479
He's not a reckless fool.

39
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:09,680
Even if he couldn't win,

40
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:11,140
he could have outrun them.

41
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,540
I hope Yueying is okay.

42
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,920
Brother and Diyun are both inside.

43
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:17,450
He will definitely be fine.

44
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:21,640
Yunyuan.

45
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:22,170
Brother.

46
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:23,360
How is Yueying?

47
00:02:23,400 --> 00:02:24,860
Lend me your Spirit Pearl.

48
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:27,000
How do you know I have a Spirit Pearl?

49
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,780
I've never shown it to anyone.

50
00:02:29,920 --> 00:02:32,180
Does Yunyuan really know me from before?

51
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:35,400
Here.

52
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:37,280
Saving Yueying is what matters.

53
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:37,940
Wait for me.

54
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:56,210
Yunyuan.

55
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,760
Are you two okay?

56
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,200
Here.

57
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:08,660
Why are you all still here?

58
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:11,880
Waiting here won't help anything.

59
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:13,400
Go back and rest.

60
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,440
We'll talk tomorrow when Yueying wakes up.

61
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,640
I'll help you back.

62
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:29,960
Where is the guest room?

63
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:31,480
I'll take you to rest.

64
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:33,360
Thank you for today.

65
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,280
It was nothing.

66
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:48,400
Sister,

67
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,280
have something to eat first.

68
00:03:50,640 --> 00:03:51,880
How is Brother doing?

69
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,880
He and Diyun are meditating in the room.

70
00:03:54,880 --> 00:03:56,079
How is Yueying?

71
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:59,480
His primordial spirit is stable now.

72
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:02,040
We dragged him back from death's door.

73
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:03,240
Don't worry.

74
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,730
He'll wake up tomorrow.

75
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:09,400
If I find out who hurt you like this,

76
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,360
I will skin them alive

77
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,640
to avenge you.

78
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:30,200
Why do I feel so uneasy?

79
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:38,600
Yunyuan.

80
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:43,920
Yunyuan, what's wrong?

81
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,120
This isn't working.

82
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,120
By my soul,

83
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:58,420
enter your spirit.

84
00:04:58,440 --> 00:04:59,560
Dragon God above,

85
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:01,580
protect your primordial spirit.

86
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,000
Ling'er.

87
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,010
Ling'er.

88
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,400
What happened?

89
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:23,800
Who hurt you?

90
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:26,000
My cultivation is lacking.

91
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:28,930
That's why I fell into the Snake Demon's trap.

92
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,410
The Snake Demon?

93
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:33,200
You mean that Flood Dragon?

94
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:35,040
He held many civilians hostage.

95
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,280
He only uses dirty tricks.

96
00:05:36,280 --> 00:05:37,600
I was careless for a moment,

97
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:38,860
and fell into his trap.

98
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:41,159
I barely escaped the barrier he set up.

99
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:42,600
That Snake Demon is cunning.

100
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,800
We only encountered his clones before.

101
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:46,640
I underestimated him this time,

102
00:05:46,960 --> 00:05:48,159
and met his true form.

103
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:51,480
I was also played for a fool by that Snake Demon.

104
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:53,159
You mean,

105
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,810
there are still many survivors there?

106
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,600
Knowing it's a Snake Demon makes it easy.

107
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,440
Let me go.

108
00:05:59,640 --> 00:06:00,360
I am his natural predator.

109
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,640
My bloodline alone can suppress him.

110
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:02,440
This time,

111
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,880
I'll skin him and make soup for Yueying.

112
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:06,560
Wait.

113
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:09,880
Qingluan.

114
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:11,960
We need to discuss this further.

115
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:14,200
Go to my room and check if Ling'er is awake first.

116
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:14,680
Okay.

117
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,040
Diyun.

118
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,800
Tell your father, the Heavenly Emperor,

119
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,800
to stop these indiscriminate divine punishments.

120
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:27,730
Stay out of this.

121
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,400
My clan receives mortal worship.

122
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:33,480
Naturally, we must slay demons

123
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,520
and uphold justice.

124
00:06:34,520 --> 00:06:35,200
Justice?

125
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:37,280
You ignore whether people live or die,

126
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:39,000
as long as you hit the demon?

127
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,640
You call this kind of divine punishment

128
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:42,080
"justice"?

129
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:45,370
If the lightning harms civilians,

130
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:46,680
the Heavenly Laws will provide punishment.

131
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:48,040
I will report this matter.

132
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:50,600
I will ensure the innocent receive justice.

133
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,760
A thousand years ago,

134
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,800
when demonic energy ravaged Kunmi,

135
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:57,420
the Heaven Clan never cared about Kunmi.

136
00:06:59,240 --> 00:06:59,800
Now,

137
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:02,530
there is no need for you to care either.

138
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,660
On this matter,

139
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:14,370
the Heaven Clan indeed acted improperly.

140
00:07:14,440 --> 00:07:14,880
Tsk.

141
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,220
Dead fish eyes.

142
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,680
"Dead fish eyes"?

143
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:26,440
Was he talking about me just now?

144
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:29,010
I'm going to teach him a lesson.

145
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,480
Rest well.

146
00:07:31,640 --> 00:07:32,900
I'm going out for a bit.

147
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,260
General, you mustn't.

148
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:48,570
The prophecy the Prophet sacrificed his life for

149
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:50,600
will surely come true.

150
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,800
Once my Lord returns,

151
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:56,330
he will unite the Three Realms.

152
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,000
Grand Protector,

153
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:02,400
when do we retrieve the Spirit Pearl?

154
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:03,840
And the Qiankun Cauldron?

155
00:08:03,840 --> 00:08:04,640
Be patient.

156
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:07,560
We must plan carefully this time.

157
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:11,080
We cannot repeat our past mistakes.

158
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,560
If the Spirit Pearl is destroyed again,

159
00:08:15,200 --> 00:08:17,640
we will never have another chance.

160
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,800
I need a plan.

161
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,400
Got it.

162
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:50,960
Help!

163
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:54,000
Help!

164
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:03,200
It's a human.

165
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:05,840
No.

166
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,840
It's a demon.

167
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,000
He's still breathing.

168
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:10,800
Hey.

169
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:11,960
Wake up.

170
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:14,880
Forget it.

171
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,160
Help!

172
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,410
Is anyone there?

173
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,000
Ling'er.

174
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,010
Ling'er.

175
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,040
Be careful.

176
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:34,440
I'm exhausted.

177
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:34,800
Ling'er.

178
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:35,460
Who is this?

179
00:09:36,040 --> 00:09:37,300
I found him by the road.

180
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,400
He's just a little demon.

181
00:09:41,680 --> 00:09:43,340
Hasn't Yunyuan returned yet?

182
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,600
That snake demon is cunning.

183
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,660
It's hard to catch.

184
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,600
This little demon likely failed his tribulation.

185
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:54,080
His cultivation was scattered by heavenly thunder.

186
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:56,210
He can barely maintain his human form.

187
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:05,840
Where am I?

188
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,560
Young man.

189
00:10:07,800 --> 00:10:09,000
What's your name?

190
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,800
Do you know that carrying you back

191
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:11,840
completely wore me out?

192
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:12,880
I'm Yinfeng.

193
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:14,840
Thank you, Sister.

194
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:17,100
I was just a small demon in the mountains.

195
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:18,600
But I had bad luck.

196
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:21,280
I got caught in a great demon's thunder tribulation.

197
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:23,080
Thank you for saving me, Sister.

198
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:24,600
I am forever grateful.

199
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,440
Haha.

200
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:26,080
Hey.

201
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:27,600
No need to thank me.

202
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:29,400
And don't think about offering yourself to me.

203
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:31,200
Just rest here and heal.

204
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:34,120
Go back to your cave and cultivate once you're better.

205
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:34,920
Yinfeng.

206
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:36,440
And I'm Nongyue.

207
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:38,290
You're just a little demon.

208
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:40,200
Why do you have such a fancy name?

209
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,000
Why are you looking at me like that?

210
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,400
As if I bullied you.

211
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:47,800
Oh, come on.

212
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:49,240
We know where he came from.

213
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,360
Don't be so mean.

214
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,690
You're scaring the kid.

215
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:53,280
Let's go.

216
00:10:53,280 --> 00:10:54,140
Come to my room.

217
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:54,960
Okay.

218
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:55,420
Sister.

219
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:56,780
Sister.

220
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:57,800
Stay close.

221
00:10:57,880 --> 00:10:59,840
I still don't know your name.

222
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,170
Just call me Sister.

223
00:11:01,880 --> 00:11:02,410
Ling'er.

224
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:03,240
Wait for me.

225
00:11:04,040 --> 00:11:04,880
Luochen said...

226
00:11:04,880 --> 00:11:07,200
...you can't just pick up men off the street.

227
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,160
Ling'er.

228
00:11:11,520 --> 00:11:12,080
Yueying.

229
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:14,890
How is your recovery coming along?

230
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:15,840
I'm fine now.

231
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:18,400
Who is that demon boy with Ling'er?

232
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:21,400
He lost his cultivation in a thunder tribulation.

233
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:23,000
Fortunately, the Princess saved him.

234
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,440
Ling'er is kind-hearted.

235
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,400
Keep an eye on him.

236
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:27,060
Investigate his background.

237
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:28,040
Yes, General.

238
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:31,800
Diyun.

239
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,000
You're still here?

240
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:33,690
Ling'er.

241
00:11:33,840 --> 00:11:35,970
You're helping Yunyuan with his work.

242
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:40,800
You know,

243
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:42,880
you're actually a pretty good guy.

244
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:44,560
When I first met you,

245
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:45,880
I thought you were totally unreliable.

246
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:47,740
But after spending time with you,

247
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:50,260
I see you're actually quite dependable.

248
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:51,400
So,

249
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:52,760
I used to be unreliable,

250
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:53,860
and undependable?

251
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:59,280
Just like an idle rich playboy.

252
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:01,800
An idle rich playboy?

253
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:02,800
Not bad.

254
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:05,680
Better than a landlord's foolish son.

255
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,000
Slow down.

256
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,080
Where's Yinfeng?

257
00:12:13,560 --> 00:12:15,690
He took his medicine and went to sleep.

258
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:19,760
I went to investigate the place he mentioned.

259
00:12:19,760 --> 00:12:22,240
There are indeed traces of a lightning tribulation nearby.

260
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,680
There was a small village there.

261
00:12:23,680 --> 00:12:26,080
It got caught in the blast. No one survived.

262
00:12:27,880 --> 00:12:28,680
Perhaps

263
00:12:29,400 --> 00:12:30,480
the great demon undergoing the tribulation

264
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:31,520
and the snake demon that attacked the village

265
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:32,450
are the same one.

266
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:36,080
The same one?

267
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,330
I'm not sure yet.

268
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:39,060
I need to look into it more.

269
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:40,840
You didn't find out for sure?

270
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:42,000
When Yinfeng wakes up,

271
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,260
I need to ask him again.

272
00:12:43,640 --> 00:12:45,600
I'm just a low-level demon.

273
00:12:46,280 --> 00:12:47,480
You're up?

274
00:12:47,800 --> 00:12:49,400
Why didn't you sleep a bit longer?

275
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:49,960
Ling'er.

276
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,480
I feel much better.

277
00:12:51,880 --> 00:12:53,560
I made some snacks.

278
00:12:57,160 --> 00:12:57,960
Diyun.

279
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,880
Just ask me.

280
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:01,400
I'll tell you everything I know.

281
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,600
I won't hold anything back.

282
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:03,400
Okay.

283
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:06,080
Tell me exactly what happened that day.

284
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:08,600
Okay.

285
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:11,660
I was cultivating in the mountains that day,

286
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,800
when lightning suddenly struck.

287
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:15,800
I was on the edge of the impact zone,

288
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:17,600
but the lightning was so powerful

289
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:19,600
that I couldn't dodge in time and got hurt.

290
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:21,680
I passed out by the roadside.

291
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,890
Luckily, Ling'er saved me.

292
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:29,000
But I didn't even see the great demon.

293
00:13:29,560 --> 00:13:30,760
So,

294
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,610
you don't know much either.

295
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:35,800
I need to go back there.

296
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:36,960
I'll go with you.

297
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,840
Evil demons like that

298
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:40,570
don't deserve to stay in Kunmi.

299
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:43,080
Yunyuan made Kunmi a place where all clans live in harmony.

300
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:44,940
We can't let these demons ruin it.

301
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:45,560
Ling'er.

302
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:47,640
You'd better stay at Yunshenbuzhichu.

303
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:49,480
But I want to help you.

304
00:13:49,880 --> 00:13:51,600
Ling'er, this is serious.

305
00:13:51,640 --> 00:13:54,000
That snake demon ran Yunyuan and me in circles.

306
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,480
If it really is that snake demon,

307
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,360
and we have to fight him,

308
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:58,200
I might not be able to protect you.

309
00:13:58,200 --> 00:13:59,600
But what if it's not the snake demon?

310
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:00,480
Yinfeng said

311
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:02,080
he was absorbing the villagers' essence.

312
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:03,040
If we let this continue,

313
00:14:03,040 --> 00:14:04,960
more innocent people will get hurt.

314
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:05,680
Ling'er.

315
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,600
Diyun is right.

316
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:09,080
Our powers are weak,

317
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,740
so we shouldn't get in the way.

318
00:14:14,760 --> 00:14:16,720
So you're afraid I'll hold you back.

319
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:17,120
No.

320
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:17,800
Ling'er.

321
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:19,000
Diyun.

322
00:14:19,160 --> 00:14:21,640
Why don't you go scout again?

323
00:14:21,640 --> 00:14:23,440
I'll stay and look after Sister.

324
00:14:23,880 --> 00:14:24,410
Yinfeng.

325
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,240
It's windy outside.

326
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:26,040
I'll walk you back to your room.

327
00:14:26,040 --> 00:14:26,600
Okay.

328
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:33,400
Is this kid doing this on purpose?

329
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,280
It's like this every time.

330
00:14:35,280 --> 00:14:36,280
He goes to hunt demons secretly by himself,

331
00:14:36,280 --> 00:14:38,080
and lies to me that they ran away.

332
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:39,280
Sister.

333
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,080
Why don't we

334
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:43,840
sneak out and go ourselves?

335
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,860
That's not a good idea.

336
00:14:46,040 --> 00:14:47,200
They're just worried about me.

337
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:48,600
If I sneak off,

338
00:14:48,640 --> 00:14:50,040
they'll be worried sick.

339
00:14:50,680 --> 00:14:53,000
How about we leave a letter before we go?

340
00:14:53,680 --> 00:14:56,560
We're just going to check the situation anyway.

341
00:14:58,680 --> 00:15:00,040
Just scouting.

342
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,840
It shouldn't be dangerous.

343
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,840
After we leave the letter,

344
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:05,880
by the time they see it, I'll already be there.

345
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:07,880
They won't be able to send me back.

346
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:10,240
That's a good idea.

347
00:15:11,040 --> 00:15:12,040
Young man,

348
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:13,400
you look a bit dull,

349
00:15:13,400 --> 00:15:15,200
but you're actually quite sharp.

350
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:16,260
It's decided then.

351
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:16,680
Okay.

352
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,460
I'll protect you, Sister.

353
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:20,640
The sooner, the better.

354
00:15:20,640 --> 00:15:21,640
Go pack up.

355
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:22,530
Okay.

356
00:15:22,800 --> 00:15:24,130
The sooner, the better.

357
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:29,400
What a naive little girl.

358
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,200
So easy to fool.

359
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:40,420
Why is it like this?

360
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:42,400
Are the demons still here?

361
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,520
I don't know either, Sister.

362
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:45,040
Maybe

363
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:47,440
we should wait for King Kunmi and Diyun.

364
00:15:48,200 --> 00:15:50,060
If that great demon is still here,

365
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:52,040
I'm afraid the two of us won't stand a chance.

366
00:15:52,040 --> 00:15:53,500
Who says I can't handle it?

367
00:15:53,880 --> 00:15:54,840
Without them,

368
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:57,040
I can still teach these demons a lesson.

369
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,200
Hey, Sister.

370
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:05,400
What a strong stench.

371
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:06,840
It seems these demons

372
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:08,290
have harmed many lives.

373
00:16:12,040 --> 00:16:13,100
Watch out, Sister.

374
00:16:19,400 --> 00:16:21,060
Such fresh spiritual energy.

375
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:23,010
Yinfeng, watch out.

376
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:42,410
Summon the Spirit Pearl, quickly!

377
00:16:42,560 --> 00:16:43,640
With my soul,

378
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:45,280
enter my spirit.

379
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:47,760
Dragon God above,

380
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:49,720
grant me success.

381
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:55,090
Something's wrong.

382
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:57,680
Why does this Spirit Pearl have no soul?

383
00:16:58,560 --> 00:16:59,490
What's going on?

384
00:17:00,920 --> 00:17:01,840
Let me check again.
